body_html: After consulting the fantastic https://tf-contrib-analyzer.herokuapp.com/, I see no uses of this on GitHub. I don't think we'd want it in core for now. It is definitely a candidate for inclusion in a repo maintained by the (to be formed) SIG-contrib.
